Content Files Properties Log.name: Content Files Properties Log
Content Files Properties Log.description: In the Content Files Properties Log Brightspace Data Set, each row represents a change (created, edited, or deleted) to a file that is linked to a content object within an org unit. The data set only captures changes to content files from July 2022 onwards. FAQ Q: Does this data set provide the size of all files within Brightspace?A: No. This data set only provides data on files associated with content objects. Additionally, it only surfaces data for newly uploaded, edited, or deleted files (associated with content) starting with the release of the data set in July 2022. It does not provide any historical data. Q: Are Active and Inactive courses included in the data?A: Yes. As long as the files are associated with a content object, it doesn't matter whether the course is active or inactive. Q: Are all file formats included in the data?A: Yes, all file formats are included when associated with a content object. However, please be aware that this data set does NOT include files that are embedded within an HTML content object. Intelligent Agent Objects.name: Intelligent Agent Objects
Intelligent Agent Objects.description: The Intelligent Agent Objects Brightspace Data Set describes all the intelligent agents created in your organization. Returned Fields

fields.description: Unique agent identifier.

Outcomes in Registries.name: Outcomes in Registries
Outcomes in Registries.description: The Outcomes in Registries Brightspace Data Set provides details of which outcomes belong to which registries for all your org units. It can be used to list all outcomes in the intent list of a course, or all the outcomes in a program. The only available data for org unit owned registries is from June 2021 onwards. All data for program registries is available, starting with your organization's first use of Learning Outcomes.

fields.name: OutcomeId
fields.description: ID of this Outcome in the Outcome Details data set.

fields.name: RegistryId
fields.description: ID of registry representing the context in which this outcome exists.

fields.name: CreatedDate
fields.description: For imported outcomes, the date that this outcome was mapped to the registry (UTC). For authored outcomes, the date this outcome was created. Field can be null.

fields.name: CreatedBy
fields.description: ID of user who imported or created the outcome in the registry. Field can be null.

fields.name: LastModifiedDate
fields.description: Date when this item was last modified (UTC). Contains created date upon creation and deleted date for deleted items.

fields.name: LastModifiedBy
fields.description: ID of user who last modified, created, or deleted this item.

fields.name: IsDeleted
fields.description: Indicates if this item has been deleted.

Outcomes Program Details.name: Outcomes Program Details
Outcomes Program Details.description: The Outcomes Program Details Brightspace Data Set provides details about the programs that are defined to hold a collection of outcomes (registry). All data for the data set is available, starting with your organization's first use of Learning Outcomes.

fields.name: ProgramId
fields.description: ID of this program which owns the registry.

fields.name: ProgramName
fields.description: The name of this program.

fields.name: OrgUnitId
fields.description: ID of the org unit which owns this program.

fields.name: CreatedDate
fields.description: Date when this item was initially created (UTC). Field can be null.

fields.name: CreatedBy
fields.description: ID of user who initially created this item. Field can be null.

fields.name: LastModifiedDate
fields.description: Date when this item was last modified (UTC). Contains created date upon creation and deleted date for deleted items.

fields.name: LastModifiedBy
fields.description: ID of user who last modified, created, or deleted this item.

fields.name: IsDeleted
fields.description: Indicates if this item has been deleted.

Outcomes Registry Owners.name: Outcomes Registry Owners
Outcomes Registry Owners.description: In the Outcomes Registry Owners Brightspace Data Set, each entry represents a registry for both program and org unit owned registries. The data set only captures data from June 2021 onwards.

fields.name: OwnerType
fields.description: Type of entity which owns this registry. Set to 1 if owner is org unit, set to 2 if owner is program.

fields.name: OwnerId
fields.description: ID or org unit owner when OwnerType is 1. ID of program when OwnerType is 2.

fields.name: RegistryId
fields.description: ID of registry for the org unit or program.

fields.name: CreatedDate
fields.description: Date when this item was initially created (UTC). Field can be null.

fields.name: CreatedBy
fields.description: ID of user who initially created this item. Field can be null.

fields.name: LastModifiedDate
fields.description: Date when this item was last modified (UTC). Contains created date upon creation and deleted date for deleted items.

fields.name: LastModifiedBy
fields.description: ID of user who last modified, created, or deleted this item.

fields.name: IsDeleted
fields.description: Indicates if this item has been deleted.

Outcomes Rubric Alignments.name: Outcomes Rubric Alignments
Outcomes Rubric Alignments.description: In the Outcomes Rubric Alignments Brightspace Data Set, each entry represents an alignment for a learning outcome to a rubric criterion row. The data set only captures data from June 2021 onwards.

fields.name: RubricId
fields.description: Unique rubric identifier.

fields.name: CriterionId
fields.description: Identifier for the criterion row of the rubric.

fields.name: OutcomeId
fields.description: Unique identifier for the outcome object.

fields.name: RegistryId
fields.description: ID of the registry for the org unit or program.

fields.name: CreatedDate
fields.description: The date when the alignment of this outcome was recorded for this rubric criterion row. Field can be null.

fields.name: CreatedBy
fields.description: ID of the user who initially created this alignment. Field can be null.

fields.name: LastModifiedDate
fields.description: Date when this item was last modified (UTC). Contains created date upon creation and deleted date for deleted items.

fields.name: LastModifiedBy
fields.description: ID of user who last modified, created, or deleted this item.

fields.name: IsDeleted
fields.description: Set to true if the outcome alignment has been removed from the rubric or the rubric has been deleted.

Outcomes Scale Definition.name: Outcomes Scale Definition
Outcomes Scale Definition.description: In the Outcomes Scale Definition Brightspace Data Set, each entry represents an achievement scale defined at the organization level. All data for the data set is available, starting with your organization's first use of Learning Outcomes.

fields.name: ScaleId
fields.description: ID for this scale.

fields.name: Name
fields.description: Name of this scale.

fields.name: IsDefault
fields.description: Indicates if this is the scale used by default whenever an assessment of an outcome takes place.

fields.name: UsePercentages
fields.description: Indicates if percentage ranges are specified for each scale level. This is used when suggesting a scale level for an assessment. Specific percentage threshold values are associated with each Scale Level.

fields.name: CreatedDate
fields.description: Date when this item was initially created (UTC). Field can be null.

fields.name: CreatedBy
fields.description: ID of user who initially created this item. Field can be null.

fields.name: LastModifiedDate
fields.description: Date when this item was last modified (UTC). Contains created date upon creation and deleted date for deleted items.

fields.name: LastModifiedBy
fields.description: ID of user who last modified, created, or deleted this item.

fields.name: IsDeleted
fields.description: Indicates if this item has been deleted.

fields.name: RegistryId
fields.description: ID of registry that owns this scale.

Outcomes Scale Level Definition.name: Outcomes Scale Level Definition
Outcomes Scale Level Definition.description: In the Outcomes Scale Level Definition Brightspace Data Set, each entry represents a scale level defined in your scales. On the evaluation UI, they are represented by a single, clickable "frame". Examples include "Not Yet Achieved", "Achieved", and "Mastered". Scale levels can't be deleted once created. Scale levels become inaccessible when their parent scale is deleted. All data for the data set is available, starting with your organization's first use of Learning Outcomes.

fields.name: ScaleLevelId
fields.description: ID for this scale level.

fields.name: ScaleId
fields.description: ID of the parent scale.

fields.name: Name
fields.description: Name of this scale level.

fields.name: SortOrder
fields.description: Determines ordering for this scale level.

fields.name: PercentageRangeStart
fields.description: The score percentage threshold boundary for this scale level. This value is used when automatically suggesting a scale level from numeric assessment results. Field can be null.

fields.name: RGB
fields.description: Color of this scale level in HTML hex notation.

fields.name: CreatedDate
fields.description: Date when this item was initially created (UTC). Field can be null.

fields.name: CreatedBy
fields.description: ID of user who initially created this item. Field can be null.

fields.name: LastModifiedDate
fields.description: Date when this item was last modified (UTC). Contains created date upon creation and deleted date for deleted items.

fields.name: LastModifiedBy
fields.description: ID of user who last modified, created, or deleted this item.

Portfolio Categories.name: Portfolio Categories
Portfolio Categories.description: The Portfolio Categories Brightspace Data Set details the categories that have been created in your organization. Returned Fields

fields.name: CategoryId
fields.description: Unique category identifier

fields.name: OrgUnitId
fields.description: Unique org unit identifier. Field can be null

fields.name: Name
fields.description: Portfolio category name.

fields.name: IsRetired
fields.description: Indicates the category is retired and therefore cannot be used.

fields.name: IsDeleted
fields.description: Indicates if the portfolio category is deleted

fields.name: LastModified
fields.description: Date when the portfolio category was last modified (UTC).

fields.name: LastModifiedBy
fields.description: User who last modified the portfolio category.

Portfolio Evidence Categories.name: Portfolio Evidence Categories
Portfolio Evidence Categories.description: The Portfolio Evidence Categories Brightspace Data Set details the one or many categories that are mapped to each piece of evidence in the Portfolios in your organization. Returned Fields

fields.name: CategoryId
fields.description: The identifier for the category

fields.name: EvidenceId
fields.description: The identifier for the evidence

fields.name: Group
fields.description: Indicates how the category was linked to the evidence. By the learner or instructor.

fields.name: IsDeleted
fields.description: Indicates whether the link between the category and the evidence is deleted

fields.name: LastModified
fields.description: Date when the portfolio category was last modified (UTC).

fields.name: LastModifiedBy
fields.description: User who last modified the portfolio category

Portfolio Evidence Log.name: Portfolio Evidence Log
Portfolio Evidence Log.description: The Portfolio Evidence Log Brightspace Data Set returns the actions that occur to each piece of evidence in the Portfolios in your organization. The first data point is from May, 2019 or your first use of the Portfolio tool, whichever is more recent. Returned Fields

fields.name: LogId
fields.description: Unique identifier for each action that occurs on each object in a portfolio.

fields.name: ParentObjectId
fields.description: Unique identifier of the evidence. Field can be null.

fields.name: ObjectId
fields.description: Unique identifier of the object where the action occurred. This is equal to ParentObjectId when the ObjectType is evidence.

fields.name: ObjectType
fields.description: Indicates what type of object the action occurred on such as the evidence itself or reflection, etc.

fields.name: UserId
fields.description: Unique user identifier.

fields.name: OrgUnitId
fields.description: Unique org unit identifier. Field can be null.

fields.name: Action
fields.description: The action that occurred: Created, Updated or Deleted.

fields.name: IsMobile
fields.description: Indicates if the action occurred on a mobile device.

fields.name: ActionDate
fields.description: Date action was completed (UTC).

Portfolio Evidence Objects.name: Portfolio Evidence Objects
Portfolio Evidence Objects.description: The Portfolio Evidence Objects Brightspace Data Set defines the attributes of each piece of evidence in Portfolios in your organization. Returned Fields

fields.name: EvidenceId
fields.description: Unique evidence identifier

fields.name: OwnerId
fields.description: The user ID that this evidence belongs to

fields.name: OrgUnitId
fields.description: Unique org unit identifier. Field can be null.

fields.name: EvidenceType
fields.description: The type of evidence

fields.name: Title
fields.description: The evidence title

fields.name: IsApproved
fields.description: Indicates the evidence is approved

fields.name: IsSpotlighted
fields.description: Indicates the evidence is spotlighted

fields.name: IsSharedToParents
fields.description: Indicates the evidence is shared to parents

fields.name: IsDeleted
fields.description: Indicates that the evidence object is deleted.

fields.name: IsRecoverableByInstructor
fields.description: Indicates that the deleted evidence object can be recovered by the instructor. Field can be null.

fields.name: LastModified
fields.description: Date when the evidence object was last modified (UTC).

fields.name: LastModifiedBy
fields.description: User who last modified the evidence object

fields.name: IsSharedWithInstructor
fields.description: Indicates the evidence is shared to instructors. Field can be null.

fields.name: DateSharedWithInstructor
fields.description: Date when the evidence was most recently shared to instructors (UTC). Field can be null.

PreRequisite Conditions Met.name: PreRequisite Conditions Met
PreRequisite Conditions Met.description: The PreRequisite Conditions Met Brightspace Data Set returns all the prerequisite conditions that have been met for applicable users in the organization. The PreRequisite Conditions Met Brightspace Data Set contains data from 1 January 2021 onwards and adheres to the default system limit of 150 million rows of the most recent data.

fields.name: PreRequisiteId
fields.description: Unique prerequisite identifier.

fields.name: UserId
fields.description: Unique user identifier.

fields.name: DateMet
fields.description: Date the prerequisite condition was met (UTC). Field can be null

fields.name: Action
fields.description: The action that occurred: Met or Deleted.

fields.name: LastModified
fields.description: The date and time when the condition was Met or Deleted. For Met conditions, this matches the DateMet column.

Release Condition Objects.name: Release Condition Objects
Release Condition Objects.description: The Release Condition Objects Brightspace Data Set returns all the release conditions (prerequisites and results) that have been created in the organization.

fields.name: PreRequisiteId
fields.description: Unique pre-requisite identifier.

fields.name: ResultId
fields.description: Unique result identifier.

fields.name: OrgUnitId
fields.description: Unique organization identifier.

fields.name: Name
fields.description: Pre-requisite condition name.

fields.name: IsNegativeCondition
fields.description: Indicates if the condition relies on something not happening.

fields.name: PreRequisiteToolId
fields.description: Unique pre-requisite tool identifier.

fields.name: Id1
fields.description: Unique identifier for the pre-requisite tool. Field can be null.

fields.name: Id2
fields.description: Secondary unique identifier for the pre-requisite tool when needed. Field can be null.

fields.name: ResultToolId
fields.description: Unique identifier for the result tool.

fields.name: UsesPercentage
fields.description: Indicates if the pre-requisite is looking at a grade percentage.

fields.name: OperatorTypeDesc
fields.description: Defines where all or any of the pre-requisites need to be met. Field can be null.

fields.name: Version
fields.description: Indicates the version of the row. This information is used to determine which table row occurred first, similar to the way time stamps function in other data sets.

fields.name: Guid1
fields.description: Unique identifier for the pre-requisite tool. For a release condition object based on Outcomes, value will match the ObjectId of the Outcome.Field can be null

fields.name: Guid2
fields.description: Unique identifier for the pre-requisite tool. For a release condition object based on Outcomes, value will match the ScaleLevelId of the Outcome.Field can be null.

Release Condition Results.name: Release Condition Results
Release Condition Results.description: The Release Condition Results Brightspace Data Set returns all the release condition results and whether they have been met for applicable users in the organization. These are the resulting actions that occur when pre-requisites are met.

fields.name: ResultId
fields.description: Unique result identifier.

fields.name: UserId
fields.description: Unique user identifier.

fields.name: Met
fields.description: Indicates whether the result has been met or not met by the user.

fields.name: Version
fields.description: Indicates the version of the row. This information is used to determine which table row occurred first, similar to the way time stamps function in other data sets.

Role Details.name: Role Details
Role Details.description: The Role Details Brightspace Data Set returns a full set of attributes for each role in your organization.

fields.name: RoleId
fields.description: Unique role identifier.

fields.name: RoleName
fields.description: Name of the role.

fields.name: Description
fields.description: Description of the role. Field can be null.

fields.name: IsCascading
fields.description: Attribute indicating that the role cascades from other roles.

fields.name: InClassList
fields.description: Attribute indicating that users with this role appear in class lists.

fields.name: ClassListRoleName
fields.description: Attribute indicating the role name for users that appear in class lists. Field can be null.

fields.name: ClassListShowGroups
fields.description: Attribute indicating that members of this role can see groups consisting of learners in the class list.

fields.name: ClassListShowSections
fields.description: Attribute indicating that members of this role can see sections consisting of learners in the class list.

fields.name: ClassListDisplayRole
fields.description: Attribute indicating that members of this role appear in the class list with the role displayed.

fields.name: AccessInactiveCO
fields.description: Attribute indicating that the role can access inactive course offerings.

fields.name: HasSpecialAccess
fields.description: Attribute indicating that the role has special access to courses.

fields.name: AddToCourseOfferingGroups
fields.description: Attribute indicating that the role appears in the course offering group.

fields.name: CanBeAutoEnrolledIntoGroups
fields.description: Attribute indicating that the role can be automatically enrolled into groups in a class.

fields.name: AddToCourseOfferingSections
fields.description: Attribute indicating that users with this role can be added to course offering sections.

fields.name: CanBeAutoEnrolledIntoSections
fields.description: Attribute indicating that users with this role can be automatically enrolled into course sections.

fields.name: AccessPastCourses
fields.description: Attribute indicating that this role can access past courses.

fields.name: AccessFutureCourses
fields.description: Attribute indicating that this role can access courses that have not yet started.

fields.name: SortOrder
fields.description: Indicates the sort order for users with this role.

fields.name: ShowInContent
fields.description: Indicates that this role should appear in Content.

fields.name: ShowInDiscussionAssess
fields.description: Indicates that this role should appear in Discussions assessments.

fields.name: ShowInDiscussionStats
fields.description: Indicates that this role should appear in Discussions statistics.

fields.name: ShowInGrades
fields.description: Indicates that this role should appear in Grades.

fields.name: ShowInAttendance
fields.description: Indicates that this role should appear in Attendance.

fields.name: AllowSelfEnrollInGroups
fields.description: Indicates that this role should have permission to self-enroll in groups.

fields.name: ShowInRegistration
fields.description: Indicates that this role should appear in registration information for a course.

fields.name: ShowInUserProgress
fields.description: Indicates that this role should appear in User Progress.

fields.name: RoleAlias
fields.description: Indicates the alias for this role. Field can be null.

fields.name: RoleCode
fields.description: Code assigned to each role for mapping to other systems or organizations. Field can be null.

fields.name: LastModifiedDate
fields.description: Date and time when the role was last modified (UTC). Field can be null.

fields.name: DeletedBy
fields.description: User identifier of the user that deleted the role. Field can be null.

SCORM Activities.name: SCORM Activities
SCORM Activities.description: The SCORM Activities Brightspace Data Set describes the activities that exist in the SCORM package. Each activity will only be known after the first user, regardless of role, attempts it. Returned Fields

fields.name: ActivityId
fields.description: Unique identifier of the SCORM activity.

fields.name: ScormObjectId
fields.description: Unique identifier for each content object.

fields.name: ParentActivityId
fields.description: Unique identifier of the parent activity. Field can be null.

fields.name: NumChildren
fields.description: Number of child activities of this activity.

fields.name: InternalId
fields.description: Unique label for the activity. Field can be null.

fields.name: Title
fields.description: The title of the activity. Field can be null.

fields.name: CompletionThreshold
fields.description: Used to determine when the activity is considered complete. Field can be null.

fields.name: PassingScore
fields.description: Scaled score required to pass the activity, between 0 and 100. Field can be null.

fields.name: PassingScoreUsed
fields.description: Whether the passing score was used to determine the learner success status. Field can be null.

fields.name: ScoreMin
fields.description: Minimum value in the range for the raw score in an activity attempt. Field can be null.

fields.name: ScoreMax
fields.description: Maximum value in the range for the raw score in an activity attempt. Field can be null.

fields.name: LastModified
fields.description: Date when the activity was last modified (UTC).

SCORM Activity Attempts.name: SCORM Activity Attempts
SCORM Activity Attempts.description: The SCORM Activity Attempts Brightspace Data Set lists each user attempt on each activity within a SCORM package, the completion status, success status, and time spent for each attempt. Returned Fields

fields.name: VisitId
fields.description: Unique identifier of the SCORM visit.

fields.name: ActivityId
fields.description: Unique identifier of the activity.

fields.name: AttemptNumber
fields.description: Number of the attempt on the objective.

fields.name: Completion
fields.description: The completion status of the learner in this attempt (UNKNOWN, COMPLETED, INCOMPLETE). Field can be null.

fields.name: Success
fields.description: The success status of the learner in this attempt (UNKNOWN, PASSED, FAILED). Field can be null.

fields.name: Score
fields.description: The score achieved by the learner in this attempt, between 0 and 100. Field can be null.

fields.name: ScoreRaw
fields.description: The raw score that the learner achieved in this attempt, between the min and max score of the activity. Field can be null.

fields.name: TimeSpent
fields.description: The time the learner spent in this attempt, in seconds. Field can be null.

fields.name: Progress
fields.description: How much of the activity was completed in this attempt, between 0 and 100. Field can be null.

fields.name: LastModified
fields.description: Date when the activity attempt was last modified (UTC).

SCORM Interaction Attempts.name: SCORM Interaction Attempts
SCORM Interaction Attempts.description: The SCORM Interaction Attempts Brightspace Data Set lists the runtime interactions for each user on the activities they have attempted, including their response and time spent. Returned Fields

fields.name: VisitId
fields.description: Unique identifier of the visit.

fields.name: InteractionId
fields.description: Unique identifier of the interaction.

fields.name: AttemptNumber
fields.description: Number of the attempt on the interaction.

fields.name: ActivityId
fields.description: Unique identifier of the activity.

fields.name: Timestamp
fields.description: Point in time at which the interaction was first made available to the learner for learner interaction and response. Field can be null.

fields.name: Response
fields.description: Data generated when a learner responds to an interaction. Field can be null.

fields.name: Result
fields.description: Judgment of the correctness of the learner response (CORRECT, INCORRECT, UNANTICIPATED, NEUTRAL). Field can be null.

fields.name: NumericResult
fields.description: Numeric judgement of the correctness of the learner response. Field can be null.

fields.name: TimeSpent
fields.description: The time the learner spent in this attempt, in seconds. Field can be null.

fields.name: LastModified
fields.description: Date when the interaction attempt was last modified (UTC).

SCORM Interaction Objectives.name: SCORM Interaction Objectives
SCORM Interaction Objectives.description: The SCORM Interaction Objectives Brightspace Data Set defines the relationship between interactions and their objectives. Returned Fields

fields.name: InteractionId
fields.description: Unique identifier of the interaction.

fields.name: ObjectiveId
fields.description: Unique identifier of the objective.

fields.name: LastModified
fields.description: Date when the activity was last modified (UTC).

SCORM Interactions.name: SCORM Interactions
SCORM Interactions.description: The SCORM Interactions Brightspace Data Set describes the runtime interactions that exist in each activity in the SCORM package. Each interaction will only be known after the first user, regardless of role, attempts it. Returned Fields

fields.name: InteractionId
fields.description: Unique identifier of the interaction.

fields.name: ActivityId
fields.description: Unique identifier for each activity.

fields.name: InternalId
fields.description: Unique label for the interaction. Field can be null.

fields.name: InteractionType
fields.description: The type of interaction (UNDEFINED, TRUEFALSE, CHOICE, FILLIN, LONGFILLIN, LIKERT, MATCHING, PERFORMANCE, SEQUENCING, NUMERIC, OTHER).

fields.name: Description
fields.description: Brief informative description of the interaction. Field can be null.

fields.name: Weighting
fields.description: Weight given to the interaction relative to other interactions. Field can be null.

fields.name: CorrectResponses
fields.description: JSON representation of an array of correct responses for this interaction. Field can be null.

fields.name: LastModified
fields.description: Date when the activity was last modified (UTC).

SCORM Objective Attempts.name: SCORM Objective Attempts
SCORM Objective Attempts.description: The SCORM Objective Attempts Brightspace Data Set outputs the score and completion information on every objective associated to the SCORM object where an attempt has been made. Returned Fields

fields.name: VisitId
fields.description: Unique identifier of the SCORM visit.

fields.name: ObjectiveId
fields.description: Unique identifier of the objective.

fields.name: AttemptNumber
fields.description: Number of the attempt on the objective.

fields.name: Score
fields.description: Number that reflects the performance of the learner on this objective, scaled to between 0 and 100. Field can be null.

fields.name: ScoreRaw
fields.description: Number that reflects the performance of the learner on this objective, relative to the min and max scores. Field can be null.

fields.name: Success
fields.description: Indicates whether the learner has mastered the objective (PASSED, FAILED, UNKNOWN). Field can be null.

fields.name: Completion
fields.description: Indicates whether the learner has completed the objective (COMPLETED, INCOMPLETE, UNKNOWN, NOT_ATTEMPTED, BROWSED). Field can be null.

fields.name: Progress
fields.description: How much of the objective was completed in this attempt, between 0 and 100. Field can be null.

fields.name: LastModified
fields.description: Date when the activity was last modified (UTC).

SCORM Objectives.name: SCORM Objectives
SCORM Objectives.description: The SCORM Objectives Brightspace Data Set describes the global, activity, and runtime interactions that exist for each SCORM package. The objectives will only be known after the first user registration or visit. Returned Fields

fields.name: ObjectiveId
fields.description: Unique identifier of the objective.

fields.name: ScormObjectId
fields.description: Unique identifier for each SCORM object.

fields.name: ObjectiveType
fields.description: Type of objective (GLOBAL, ACTIVITY, RUNTIME).

fields.name: ActivityId
fields.description: Unique identifier for each activity. Field can be null.

fields.name: InternalId
fields.description: Unique label for the objective. Field can be null.

fields.name: IsPrimary
fields.description: Whether this is the primary objective of the activity. Field can be null.

fields.name: Description
fields.description: Brief informative description of the objective. Field can be null.

fields.name: ScoreMin
fields.description: Minimum value, for the objective, in the range for the raw score. Field can be null.

fields.name: ScoreMax
fields.description: Maximum value, for the objective, in the range for the raw score. Field can be null.

fields.name: LastModified
fields.description: Date when the activity was last modified (UTC).

SCORM Objects.name: SCORM Objects
SCORM Objects.description: The SCORM Objects Brightspace Data Set describes all the SCORM objects that exist, and which course and which topic they are located in. At time of launch, this data set contains data from July 2020 onwards. Remaining baseline data will be filled in upon a future release. Returned Fields

fields.name: ScormObjectId
fields.description: Unique identifier of the SCORM object.

fields.name: OrgUnitId
fields.description: Unique org unit identifier.

fields.name: ContentObjectId
fields.description: Unique identifier of the content topic.

fields.name: ContentServiceContentId
fields.description: Unique identifier for the associated content in content service.

fields.name: ContentServiceRevisionId
fields.description: Unique identifier of the associated revision in content service.

fields.name: ContentServiceTopicId
fields.description: Unique identifier of the associated topic in content service.

fields.name: Title
fields.description: The title of the SCORM object. Field can be null.

fields.name: Description
fields.description: The description of the SCORM package. Field can be null.

fields.name: LearningStandard
fields.description: The learning standard used by the SCORM content, one of SCORM_11, SCORM_12, SCORM_2004_2ND_EDITION, SCORM_2004_3RD_EDITION, SCORM_2004_4TH_EDITION, AICC, XAPI, CMI5. Field can be null.

fields.name: LastModified
fields.description: Date when the SCORM content was last modified (UTC).

fields.name: LastModifiedBy
fields.description: User that last modified this SCORM object.

SCORM Visits.name: SCORM Visits
SCORM Visits.description: The SCORM Visits Brightspace Data Set lists each user visit on each SCORM object, the overall completion status, and time spent on the visit. Returned Fields

fields.name: VisitId
fields.description: Unique identifier for each SCORM visit.

fields.name: ScormObjectId
fields.description: Unique identifier of the SCORM object.

fields.name: UserId
fields.description: User associated with the SCORM visit.

fields.name: OrgUnitId
fields.description: Unique org unit identifier.

fields.name: FirstAccessDate
fields.description: The date the user first accessed the SCORM object. Field can be null.

fields.name: LastAccessDate
fields.description: The date the user last accessed the SCORM object. Field can be null.

fields.name: CompletedDate
fields.description: The date the user first completed the SCORM object. Field can be null.

fields.name: Completion
fields.description: The completion status of the user for the SCORM object. One of UNKNOWN, COMPLETED, or INCOMPLETE. Field can be null.

fields.name: Success

System Access Log.name: System Access Log
System Access Log.description: The System Access Log Brightspace Data Set captures each time a user accesses the system from the LMS via a browser (Brightspace), from the Pulse app (Pulse), or from the Brightspace Parent & Guardian mobile app (BPG-mobile). System access using Brightspace Parent & Guardian is represented in the data set twice: one where Source=Brightspace and one where Source=BPG-mobile. System access begins when the user logs in, returns after 30 minutes of inactivity, or opens the app. System access ends after 30 minutes of inactivity. Course Access.name: Course Access

fields.description: Assignment name

fields.name: Category
fields.description: Assignment category. Field can be null.

fields.name: Type
fields.description: Individual/group assignment

fields.name: GradeItemId
fields.description: Unique grade item identifier. Field can be null.

fields.name: PossibleScore
fields.description: Possible score a user can achieve on the assignment. Field can be null.

fields.name: StartDate
fields.description: Assignment availability start date (UTC). Field can be null.

fields.name: EndDate
fields.description: Assignment availability end date (UTC). Field can be null.

fields.name: DueDate
fields.description: Assignment due date (UTC). Field can be null.

fields.name: IsRestricted
fields.description: Is assignment restricted

fields.name: IsDeleted
fields.description: Is assignment deleted

fields.name: TurnItInEnabled
fields.description: Is TurnItIn enabled

fields.name: IsHidden
fields.description: True or false value indicating whether the assignment is hidden.

fields.name: SortOrder
fields.description: Display sort order used for the content objects

fields.name: SubmissionType
fields.description: Indicates the format submission type for the assignment being submitted. Values for this column include File, Text, On Paper, and Observed.

fields.name: CompletionType
fields.description: Indicates how the assignment was completed. Values for this column include OnSubmission, DueDate, ManuallyByLearner, and OnEvaluation.

fields.name: ResultId
fields.description: Unique release condition result identifier. Field can be null.

fields.name: CategoryId
fields.description: Unique category identifier for the assignment. Field can be null.

fields.name: Version
fields.description: Indicates the version of the row. This information is used to determine which table row occurred first, similar to the way time stamps function in other data sets.

fields.name: StartDateAvailabilityType
fields.description: Determines whether learners can view or access the assignment before the StartDate. Refer to About Availability Type for details. All assignments with start dates created before December 2022/20.22.12 have default value '0'. Field can be null.

fields.name: EndDateAvailabilityType
fields.description: Determines whether learners can view or access the assignment after the EndDate. Refer to About Availability Type for details. All assignments with end dates created before December 2022/20.22.12 have default value '0'. Field can be null.

fields.name: AIUtilization
fields.description: Indicates whether D2L Lumi (Brightspace AI) capabilities were used and the level of AI involvement. Possible values: 0 - No AI capabilities were involved. 1 - Generated by AI and reviewed by a human. 2 - Generated by AI and edited by a human. 3 - Assisted or uplifted by AI. 4 - Generated by AI but not yet reviewed by a human.

fields.name: Instructions
fields.description: Instructions that are shown to the learner in the submission page. Field can be null.

TurnItIn Submissions.name: TurnItIn Submissions
TurnItIn Submissions.description: The TurnItIn Submissions Brightspace Data Set returns details of assignment submissions shared with TurnItIn version 2.

fields.name: DropboxId
fields.description: Unique assignment identifier.

fields.name: SubmissionId
fields.description: Unique assignment submission identifier.

fields.name: FileId
fields.description: Unique file identifier.

fields.name: LastSubmissionDate
fields.description: Most recent submission time stamp (UTC). Field can be null.

fields.name: SubmissionStatus
fields.description: Status of assignment submission. Possible values:0 - Assignment has not been submitted.1 - Assignment is pending retrieval.2 - Assignment has been submitted.3 - An error has occurred4 - Assignment is pending Originality report.5 - Assignment's Originality report is complete.6 - Assignment has been deleted.7 - The assignment's deletion has been canceled.

fields.name: SubmissionErrorType
fields.description: Type of submission error.

fields.name: ErrorMessage
fields.description: Error message upon submission if applicable. Field can be null.

fields.name: SubmittedBy
fields.description: UserId of user who submitted the assignment to TurnItIn. Field can be null.

fields.name: LastRefreshDate
fields.description: Most recent submission refresh time stamp (UTC). Field can be null.

fields.name: LastModified
fields.description: Last time the submission was modified (UTC). Field can be null.

LTI Advantage Deployment Audit.name: LTI Advantage Deployment Audit
LTI Advantage Deployment Audit.description: The LTI Advantage Deployment Audit Brightspace Data Set logs the details of each time a user creates, updates, or deletes an LTI deployment. The data set captures events from October 2019 onwards.

fields.name: Action
fields.description: The action completed by the event: Deployed, Updated, or Deleted.

fields.name: DeploymentID
fields.description: Unique identifier for the LTI Advantage deployment.

fields.name: ClientID
fields.description: Unique identifier used in OAuth2 authentication, assigned by the platform when the LTI tool is registered.

fields.name: DeploymentName
fields.description: The name for the deployment.

fields.name: IsDeploymentEnabled
fields.description: If false, it is not possible to do any launches for this tool or make any API calls for the extensions.

fields.name: HasAssignmentsAndGrades
fields.description: If true, the Assignments and grades services (AGS) extension is enabled for this deployment.

fields.name: HasDeepLinking
fields.description: If true, the Deep Linking extension is enabled for this deployment.

fields.name: HasNamesAndRoles
fields.description: If true, the Names and Roles Provisioning Services (NPRS) extension is enabled for this deployment.

fields.name: HasSubmissionReview
fields.description: If true, the Submission Review extension is enabled for this deployment.

fields.name: HasActivityItemProfile
fields.description: If true, the Activity Item Profile extension is enabled for this deployment.

fields.name: HasPlatformNotificationService
fields.description: If true, the Platform Notification Service is enabled for this deployment.

fields.name: HasContextCopy
fields.description: If true, the Context Copy message is enabled for this deployment. The Platform Notification Service must also be enabled.

fields.name: ModifiedBy
fields.description: The ID of the Brightspace user that modified the deployment record.

fields.name: Anonymous
fields.description: If true, no user information is sent during launch.

fields.name: PreProvisioningEnabled
fields.description: If true, all users in the course are included whether they have performed a launch or not. If false, only users that have performed a launch are included for NRPS and AGS Services.

fields.name: SendOrgUnitInfo
fields.description: If true, Org Unit Id, Course Name, Course Code, Org Unit Type, LIS Course Offering Sourcedid, and LIS Course Section Sourcedid can be included in the launch.

fields.name: SendUserFirstName
fields.description: If true, user first name can be sent during launch.

fields.name: SendUserMiddleName
fields.description: If true, user middle name is included in the data sent via NPRS.

fields.name: SendUserLastName
fields.description: If true, user last name can be sent during launch.

fields.name: SendUserEmail
fields.description: If true, user email address can be sent during launch.

fields.name: SendBrightspaceUserID
fields.description: If true, D2L user ID can be sent during launch.

fields.name: SendBrightspaceUsername
fields.description: If true, D2L username is sent during launch.

fields.name: SendBrightspaceOrgDefinedId
fields.description: If true, D2L Org Defined ID can be sent for this deployment.

fields.name: SendLinkTitle
fields.description: If true, LTI Link Title is sent during launch.

fields.name: SendLinkDescription
fields.description: If true, LTI Link Description is sent during launch.

fields.name: OpenAsExternal
fields.description: If true, the majority of new links created under the deployment open in an external window. If false, new links open inline.

fields.name: AutoMigrateLinks
fields.description: If true, automatic migration can occur for links that match this deployment.

fields.name: IsSharedToManyOrgUnits
fields.description: If true, the deployment is shared to multiple org units.

fields.name: AutoCreateGrades
fields.description: If true, the Auto Create Grade Items setting is enabled.

fields.name: IncludeInFinalGrade
fields.description: If true, grades created by LTI links for this deployment are included in the final grade calculation.

fields.name: Timestamp
fields.description: Date and time (UTC) when the user created or modified the deployment.

fields.name: HasAssetProcessor
fields.description: If true, the Asset Processor Services are enabled for this deployment. The Platform Notification Service and Deeplinking must also be enabled.

LTI Advantage Registration Audit.name: LTI Advantage Registration Audit
LTI Advantage Registration Audit.description: The LTI Advantage Registration Audit Brightspace Data Set logs the details of each time a user creates, updates, or deletes an LTI registration. The data set captures events from June 2019 onwards.

fields.name: Action
fields.description: The action completed by the event: Registered, Updated, or Deleted.

fields.name: ClientId
fields.description: Unique customer facing identifier assigned by the platform when the LTI tool is registered.

fields.name: ToolName
fields.description: The name of the external learning tool.

fields.name: Domain
fields.description: Domain for the registered tool.

fields.name: RedirectURLs
fields.description: List of Redirect URLs provided by the tool, formatted as comma-separated values (CSV) list. The list is truncated to the max length allowed in the BDS field.

fields.name: KeysetURL
fields.description: The Keyset URL needed to complete the launch. The value is truncated to the max length allowed in the BDS field. Field can be null.

fields.name: LoginURL
fields.description: The Initial LTI login request endpoint as by the tool. The value is truncated to the max length allowed in the BDS field.

fields.name: LTIVersion
fields.description: Indicates whether the registration is for LTI 1.1 or LTI 1.3.

fields.name: IsRegistrationEnabled
fields.description: If true, the tool registration is enabled for the organization.

fields.name: SendInstitutionRole
fields.description: If true, the registration includes both contextual and institutional roles. If false, the registration only includes contextual roles.

fields.name: TargetLinkURI
fields.description: Optional Target Link URI used during the Deep Linking workflow when the tool doesn't provide a launch URL for the returned LTI Resource Link. Field can be null.

fields.name: ModifiedBy
fields.description: The ID of the Brightspace user that updated the tool registration data.

fields.name: HasAssignmentAndGradeServices
fields.description: If true, the Assignments and grades services (AGS) extension is enabled for this registration.

fields.name: HasSubmissionReview
fields.description: If true, the Submission Review extension is enabled for this registration.

fields.name: HasDeepLinking
fields.description: If true, the Deep Linking extension is enabled for this registration.

fields.name: HasNamesAndRoleProvisioningServices
fields.description: If true, the Names and Roles Provisioning Services (NPRS) extension is enabled for this registration.

fields.name: HasActivityItemProfile
fields.description: If true, the Activity Item Profile extension is enabled for this registration.

fields.name: HasPlatformNotificationService
fields.description: If true, the Platform Notification Service is enabled for this registration.

fields.name: Timestamp
fields.description: Date and time (UTC) when the user created or modified the registration.

LTI Launches.name: LTI Launches
LTI Launches.description: The LTI Launches Brightspace Data Set logs details of each time a user launches an LTI link in the organization.

fields.name: LTILaunchId
fields.description: Unique identifier for each individual launch.

fields.name: UserId
fields.description: The user who performed this launch.

fields.name: IMSRoleNames
fields.description: A list of user's IMS roles.

fields.name: ImpersonatingUserId
fields.description: The impersonating user who performed this launch. Field can be null.

fields.name: ImpersonatingUserIMSRoleNames
fields.description: A list of impersonating user's IMS roles. Field can be null.

fields.name: LaunchDate
fields.description: The UTC time when this launch occurred.

fields.name: OrgUnitId
fields.description: Id of the org unit where this launch happened.

fields.name: LTILinkId
fields.description: The id of the link that was used for the LTI launch. Field can be null.

fields.name: DeploymentId
fields.description: The unique identifier of the link's deployment that was used for the LTI launch. This is only available for LTI 1.3 links. Field can be null.

fields.name: ClientId
fields.description: The unique identifier of the link's registration that was used for the LTI launch. This is only available for LTI 1.3 links. Field can be null.

fields.name: ToolProviderId
fields.description: The id of the link's tool provider that was used for the LTI launch. This is only available for LTI 1.1 links. Field can be null.

fields.name: ContentTopicId
fields.description: Id of the content topic where this launch happened. Field can be null.

fields.name: ParentModuleId
fields.description: Id of the parent module where this launch happened. Field can be null.

fields.name: Placement
fields.description: Placement type of this launch. Field can be null.

fields.name: MessageVersion
fields.description: LTI message version of this launch. Field can be null.

fields.name: RequestType
fields.description: LTI request type of this launch. Field can be null.

LTI Link Migration Audit.name: LTI Link Migration Audit
LTI Link Migration Audit.description: The LTI Link Migration Audit Brightspace Data Set logs all attempted LTI link migrations. Each row in the data set represents an attempted link migration from LTI 1.1 to LTI 1.3.

fields.name: LTIMigrationId
fields.description: Unique identifier for each individual link migration

fields.name: UserId
fields.description: ID of the person who triggered the migration

fields.name: MigrationDate
fields.description: The date the migration occurred for this link (UTC)

fields.name: OrgUnitId
fields.description: ID of the org unit where the launch migration occurred

fields.name: LinkId
fields.description: ID of the link that was migrated

fields.name: LinkURL
fields.description: Launch URL for the link

fields.name: LinkName
fields.description: Name of the link

fields.name: ClientId
fields.description: ID of the registration this link was migrated to. Field can be null.

fields.name: RegistrationDomain
fields.description: Domain of the registration this link was migrated to. Field can be null.

fields.name: DeploymentId
fields.description: ID of the link's deployment that was used for the LTI migration. Field can be null.

fields.name: JobId
fields.description: ID for the job this link was migrated under.

fields.name: Status
fields.description: Status result for this link migration. Possible values: 0 = Success 1 = Error 2 = Not Found

fields.name: FailureCode
fields.description: Error code for failed migrations. Possible values: 0 = Registration Not Found 1 = Deployment Not Enabled 2 = Deployment Not Found 3 = Link Not Found 4 = Link Not Legacy 5 = Link URL Invalid 6 = Unknown 7 = Auto Migrate is not enabled in the deployment Field can be null.

fields.name: MigrationType
fields.description: How migration was triggered. Possible values: 0 = Link API 1 = Copy Course 2 = Course Migration Button 3 = Course Migration API

fields.name: LegacyURL
fields.description: The legacy domain the link was migrated from. Only populates if the legacy domain is different than the registration domain. Field can be null.

LTI Links.name: LTI Links
LTI Links.description: The LTI Links Brightspace Data Set retrieves the list of LTI links that exist in the organization. Links deleted after October 2023 are identified by the IsDeleted column. Links deleted before October 2023 are not included in the data.

fields.name: LtiLinkId
fields.description: Unique identifier for the LTI link.

fields.name: OrgUnitId
fields.description: Identifier for the Org Unit where the link was created.

fields.name: Title
fields.description: The title of the link.

fields.name: LinkType
fields.description: The type of link, either being a basic LTI launch or a CIM/Deep Linking launch to retrieve content from a tool. (0 = Basic LTI Launch, 1 = Content Item Message or Deeplinking).

fields.name: LTIVersion
fields.description: Indicates whether the link is LTI 1.1 or LTI 1.3.

fields.name: Url
fields.description: The URL used during the launch. Field can be null.

fields.name: Description
fields.description: Description of the LTI link. Field can be null.

fields.name: IsVisible
fields.description: Determines if the link is displayed when adding to course content in the course. For LTI 1.1, this is called IsVisible in the UI.

fields.name: SendTCInfo
fields.description: If true, determines if the tool_consumer variables are allowed to be included in the LTI launch. LTI 1.1 only.

fields.name: SendContextInfo
fields.description: If true, determines if context_id, context_title, context_label, and context_type variables are included in the LTI launch. LTI 1.1 only.

fields.name: SendCourseInfo
fields.description: If true, determines if LISSourcedId is included in the launch. LTI 1.1 only.

fields.name: SendOrgUnitInfo
fields.description: If true, determines if Org Unit Id, Course Name, Course Code, Org Unit Type, LIS Course Offering Sourcedid, and LIS Course Section Sourcedid are included in the LTI launch. LTI 1.3 only. Field can be null.

fields.name: SendUserId
fields.description: If true, determines a unique identifier for the user, generated on the user's first launch. LTI 1.1 only. This is always sent to LTI 1.3 and cannot be turned off unless Anonymous launch is used.

fields.name: SendUserName
fields.description: If true, determines if users first, last, and given name (first last) are sent during launch.

fields.name: SendUserEmail
fields.description: If true, determines if the user's primary email is sent during launch.

fields.name: SendLinkTitle
fields.description: If true, determines if the LTI Link Title is sent during launch. LTI 1.1 only.

fields.name: SendLinkDescription
fields.description: If true, determines if the LTI Link Description is sent during launch. LTI 1.1 only.

fields.name: SendD2LUserName
fields.description: If true, determines if the Brightspace username is sent during launch.

fields.name: SendD2LOrgDefinedId
fields.description: If true, determines if the Brightspace OrgDefinedId is sent during launch.

fields.name: SendD2LOrgRoleId
fields.description: If true, determines if the custom Brightspace D2L role is sent during launch. LTI 1.1 only.

fields.name: SendBrightspaceUserId
fields.description: If true, determines if the D2L User Id is sent during the launch. LTI 1.3 only. Field can be null.

fields.name: Anonymous
fields.description: If true, no user information is sent during the launch. LTI 1.3 only. Field can be null.

fields.name: Shared
fields.description: Indicates whether the link is shared with additional org units or not. Field can be null.

fields.name: UseToolProviderSecuritySettings
fields.description: If true, uses the Tool Provider security settings versus link security settings based on domain matching. LTI 1.1 only.

fields.name: LastModifiedDate
fields.description: The last time a link was updated. Field can be null.

fields.name: OuAvailabilitySetId
fields.description: Unique sharing identifier. Can be used to join on LTI Links Shared. Field can be null.

fields.name: LastModifiedBy
fields.description: User ID of user who last modified the LTI link.

fields.name: IsDeleted
fields.description: Indicates if the LTI link is deleted.

fields.name: CreatedDate
fields.description: The date the link was created (UTC). Field can be null.

fields.name: DeploymentId
fields.description: Deployment ID the link belongs to. Field can be null.

fields.name: LinkSubType
fields.description: Additional details about the link. Possible values: 1 = Basic launch 2 = Widget 3 = Deep Linking Quicklink 4 = Deep Linking Insert Stuff 5 = Deep Linking Quiz Builder 6 = Deep Linking Quiz Question 7 = Nav Bar 8 = Asset Processor Assignments 9 = Asset Processor report 10 = Asset Processor EULA 11 = Asset Processor Settings Field can be null.

Quiz Attempts.name: Quiz Attempts
Quiz Attempts.description: The Quiz Attempts Brightspace Data Set returns details for each user quiz attempt for all your org units. This data set includes completed quiz attempts and in-progress quiz attempts.

fields.name: AttemptId
fields.description: Unique attempt identifier

fields.name: QuizId
fields.description: Unique quiz identifier

fields.name: UserId
fields.description: Unique user identifier

fields.name: OrgUnitId
fields.description: Unique org unit identifier

fields.name: AttemptNumber
fields.description: Attempt number for the quiz

fields.name: TimeStarted
fields.description: Quiz attempt start time (UTC).

fields.name: TimeCompleted
fields.description: Quiz attempt completion time (UTC). Field can be null.

fields.name: Score
fields.description: Score for the attempt. Field can be null.

fields.name: IsGraded
fields.description: If a quiz has been graded

fields.name: OldAttemptNumber
fields.description: Number of previous times a learner has attempted the quiz. Field can be null.

fields.name: IsDeleted
fields.description: Indicates that the quiz attempt is deleted. Field can be null.

fields.name: PossibleScore
fields.description: Indicates the total possible value of the quiz attempt. This should indicate what the quiz "out of" score is, even if the quiz total possible value changes after the attempt is made. Field can be null.

fields.name: IsRetakeIncorrectOnly
fields.description: Indicates if this attempt only includes questions that were incorrect on a previous attempt.

fields.name: DueDate
fields.description: Quiz attempt due date (UTC). Based on when the learner begins the attempt, even if the instructor changes the quiz due date later. This does not take any special access time limit into account. Field can be null.

fields.name: TimeLimit
fields.description: Amount of time, in minutes, that a learner has to complete the quiz attempt. Based on when the learner begins the attempt, even if the instructor changes the quiz time limit later. This does not take any special access time limit into account. Field can be null.

fields.name: TimeLimitEnforced
fields.description: Indicates whether the time limit on this quiz attempt is enforced. Based on when the learner begins the attempt, even if the instructor changes the time limit enforced setting later. Field can be null.

fields.name: TimeLimitExceededBehaviour
fields.description: If the time limit is enforced for this attempt, indicates the desired behavior when the time limit is exceeded. Field can be null.

fields.name: IsSynchronous
fields.description: Indicates that a quiz attempt is synchronous. A synchronous quiz's timer starts on the start date.

fields.name: DeductionPercentage
fields.description: The percentage of a question's point value that is deducted from the quiz attempt score if the question is answered incorrectly. This value remains constant once the learner begins the attempt, even if the instructor changes the deduction percentage later. Field can be null.

fields.name: Version
fields.description: Indicates the version of the row. This information is used to determine which table row occurred first, similar to the way timestamps function in other data sets.

Quiz Attempts Log.name: Quiz Attempts Log
Quiz Attempts Log.description: The Quiz Attempts Log Brightspace Data Set returns details on the events that occur during a quiz attempt. This data set includes completed quiz attempts, in-progress quiz attempts, and preview attempts. The IsDeleted value is always TRUE for preview attempts. There is no explicit time cap placed on this data set. However, data is sorted from newest to oldest and older data will be dropped if the data set reaches the row limit.

fields.name: LogId
fields.description: Unique log identifier

fields.name: AttemptId
fields.description: Unique attempt identifier

fields.name: EventTypeId
fields.description: Unique event type identifier

fields.name: Name
fields.description: Name of the event.

fields.name: Description
fields.description: Description of the event. Field can be null.

fields.name: EventTime
fields.description: Date and time the event occurred (UTC).

fields.name: IPAddress
fields.description: IPAddress at which the event occurred. Field may be null for quiz submit events where the quiz was auto-submitted.

fields.name: UserId
fields.description: ID of the user who initiated the quiz attempt.

fields.name: IsDeleted
fields.description: Indicates if the preview attempt has been deleted.

Quiz Objects.name: Quiz Objects
Quiz Objects.description: The Quiz Objects Brightspace Data Set returns information about the settings and properties of a quiz.

fields.name: QuizId
fields.description: Unique quiz identifier

fields.name: QuizName
fields.description: Quiz name

fields.name: QuizDescription
fields.description: Description of the Quiz. Field can be null.

fields.name: QuizCategory
fields.description: Name of category quiz is assigned to. Field can be null.

fields.name: IsActive
fields.description: Indicates if the quiz is active

fields.name: OrgUnitId
fields.description: Org unit identifier associated with the quiz object

fields.name: StartDate
fields.description: First time the quiz is visible. Field can be null.

fields.name: EndDate
fields.description: Last date the quiz is visible. Field can be null.

fields.name: DueDate
fields.description: Date the quiz is due (UTC). Field can be null.

fields.name: CreationDate
fields.description: Date the quiz was created (UTC).

fields.name: CreatedBy
fields.description: Id of the user who created the quiz. Field can be null.

fields.name: LastModified
fields.description: Date when the quiz was last modified (UTC).

fields.name: LastModifiedBy
fields.description: Id of the user who last modified the quiz. Field can be null.

fields.name: GradeObjectId
fields.description: Grade object identifier associated with the quiz. Field can be null.

fields.name: OverallScoreCalculation
fields.description: Quiz score calculation method. Types include: Highest Attempt, Lowest Attempt, Average of all attempts, First Attempt, and Last Attempt. Field can be null.

fields.name: QuizScoreDenominator
fields.description: Denominator for the quiz score

fields.name: HasPassword
fields.description: Indicates if a password is required to access this quiz. Field can be null.

fields.name: IPRestricted
fields.description: Indicates if this quiz is available only to certain IP Addresses. Field can be null.

fields.name: TimeLimit
fields.description: Time limit for the quiz in minutes.

fields.name: TimeLimitEnforced
fields.description: Indicates if the time limit assigned to the quiz is enforced.

fields.name: AttemptsAllowed
fields.description: Number of times learners are permitted to attempt the quiz. Null indicates unlimited attempts.

fields.name: PreventMovingBackwards
fields.description: Indicates if learners are permitted to move to previous pages in the quiz.

fields.name: AllowHints
fields.description: Indicates that there are hints allowed for the quiz.

fields.name: NotificationEmail
fields.description: Indicates that there is a notification email for this quiz if present. Field can be null.

fields.name: DisablePagerAccess
fields.description: Indicates that learners cannot access the pager functionality

fields.name: DisplayInCalendar
fields.description: Indicates if the quiz is displayed in the Calendar. Field can be null.

fields.name: IsAttemptRldb
fields.description: Indicates if Respondus LockDown Browser is required to attempt this quiz.

fields.name: IsSubviewRldb
fields.description: Indicates if Respondus LockDown Browser is required to see quiz results (submission view).

fields.name: SortOrder
fields.description: Display sort order for quizzes (when not alphabetical).

fields.name: CategoryId
fields.description: Unique category identifier for the quiz. Field can be null.

fields.name: ResultId
fields.description: Unique release condition result identifier. Field can be null.

fields.name: IsRetakeIncorrectOnly
fields.description: Indicates if the quiz allows Retake Incorrect Only.

fields.name: PagingTypeId
fields.description: Exposes page break information. Possible values: NULL = Uses Classic Quiz Creation paging 0 = All questions on one page 1 = One question per page 2 = Page breaks after each section 3 = 5 questions per page 4 = 10 questions per page Field can be null.

fields.name: IsSynchronous
fields.description: Indicates that a quiz is synchronous. A synchronous quiz's timer starts on the start date.

fields.name: DeductionPercentage
fields.description: The percentage of a question's point value that will be deducted from the quiz attempt score if the question is answered incorrectly. Field can be null.

fields.name: AIStudySupport
fields.description: Indicates if D2L Lumi Study Support is enabled for the quiz.

fields.name: HideQuestionPoints
fields.description: Indicates that the quiz has Hide Question Points enabled.

Quiz Survey Sections.name: Quiz Survey Sections
Quiz Survey Sections.description: The Quiz Survey Sections Brightspace Data Set returns information about all the sections and question pools that have been created in quizzes in the organization.

fields.name: CollectionId
fields.description: Unique question collection identifier

fields.name: SectionId
fields.description: Unique section identifier.

fields.name: Name
fields.description: Name of the section (title). Field can be null.

fields.name: NameIsDisplayed
fields.description: Indicates if the section name (title) is hidden or shown. Values are 0 for hidden, and 1 for shown.

fields.name: IsQuestionPool
fields.description: Indicates if the section is a question pool.

fields.name: SectionText
fields.description: Section text. Field can be null.

fields.name: SectionTextIsHTML
fields.description: Indicates if the section text is HTML or plain text.

fields.name: IsSectionTextHidden
fields.description: Indicates if the section text is hidden or shown. Values are 0 for hidden, and 1 for shown.

fields.name: QuestionPoints
fields.description: Number of points the section is worth when the section is a question pool. Sections that are not question pools will show as null. Field can be null.

fields.name: NumQuestions
fields.description: Indicates the number of questions in the section if the section is a question pool. If the section is not a question pool, 0 is displayed.

fields.name: NumChoices
fields.description: Indicates the number of choices in the question pool (pool size).

fields.name: Shuffle
fields.description: Indicates that the questions in the section are shuffled. Not to be confused with a question pool; a shuffled section displays the questions shuffled randomly.

fields.name: CreationDate
fields.description: Date the section was created (UTC).

fields.name: CreatedBy
fields.description: Id of the user who created the section. Field can be null.

fields.name: LastModified
fields.description: Date when the section was last modified (UTC).

fields.name: LastModifiedBy
fields.description: Id of the user who last modified the section. If questions are imported into the section, this will be null. Field can be null.

fields.name: IsDeleted
fields.description: Indicates that the section is deleted. Field can be null.

Quiz User Answer Responses.name: Quiz User Answer Responses
Quiz User Answer Responses.description: The Quiz User Answer Responses Brightspace Data Set returns details on how a user answered a specific quiz question. Data includes whether an answer is correct and details around the quiz score. Rows in the data set are filtered out if they are associated with deleted quiz questions. The Quiz User Answer Responses Brightspace Data Set contains data from 1 January 2021 onwards and adheres to the default system limit of 150 million rows of the most recent data.

fields.name: AttemptId

fields.name: AttemptNumber

fields.name: SortOrder

fields.name: UserSelection

fields.name: UserAnswer

fields.name: FileSetId

fields.name: IsDeleted

Rubrics Edit.name: Rubrics Edit
Rubrics Edit.description: In the Rubrics Edit Brightspace Data Set, each row represents one element of a rubric that was changed by a permissioned user. If multiple elements are changed in the same rubric, multiple data rows will appear in the data set. Modified Object Type Lookup The following table contains all possible ModifiedObjectType values and their corresponding rubric element:

fields.name: AuditLogId
fields.description: Unique identifier

fields.name: RubricId
